{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"An effect lifecycle change","anchor":"An-effect-lifecycle-change","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In previous versions of the Composable Architecture, a root store’s effects continued to run even"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"after the store’s lifetime. In 1.18, this leak has been fixed, and a root store’s effects will be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cancelled when the store deallocates."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you depend on a store’s fire-and-forget effect to outlive the store, for example if you want to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"ensure an analytics or persistence effect proceeds without cancellation, perform this work in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"unstructured task, instead:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"diff","code":[" return .run { _ in","-  await analytics.track(\/* ... *\/)","+  Task {","+    await analytics.track(\/* ... *\/)","+  }"," }"]},{"type":"heading","text":"A UIKit navigation helper","anchor":"A-UIKit-navigation-helper","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Our ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-navigation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" library ships with many","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"UIKit tools, and the Composable Architecture integrates with many of them, but up till now it has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"lacked support for trait-based navigation by pushing an element of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/StackState","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This has been fixed with a new endpoint on the ","type":"text"},{"code":"push","type":"